#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Hypervisor Security"
msgstr "配置 Hypervisor 安全性"

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Security</guilabel> screen is used to change the <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> password for both local and remote access. SSH password authentication is also enabled or disabled via this screen."
msgstr ""

# Tag: title
#. Tag: title
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Enable SSH Password Authentication"
msgstr "啟用 SSH 密碼認證"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "To enable SSH password authentication for remote access select the <guilabel>Enable ssh password authentication</guilabel> option and press <keycap> Space</keycap> to toggle it to enabled."
msgstr "若要啟用 SSH 密碼認證，以進行遠端存取，請選擇「<guilabel>啟用 ssh 密碼認證</guilabel>」選項，並按下 <keycap>Space</keycap>，以將它切換為啟用。"

# Tag: title
#. Tag: title
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Change <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> Password"
msgstr "更改 <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> 密碼"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the desired <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> password in the <guilabel>Password</guilabel> field. You should use a strong password."
msgstr "請在「<guilabel>密碼</guilabel>」欄位中輸入欲使用的 <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> 密碼。您應使用一組安全性較高的密碼。"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Strong passwords contain a mix of uppercase, lowercase, numeric and punctuation characters. They are six or more characters long and do not contain dictionary words."
msgstr "高安全性的密碼包含了大小寫字母、數字與標點符號字元的組合。它們必須包含六或更多個字元，並且不包含任何字字彙。"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the desired <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> password in the <guilabel>Confirm Password</guilabel> field. Ensure that the value entered in the <guilabel>Confirm Password</guilabel> field matches the value entered in the <guilabel>Password</guilabel> field exactly. Where this is not the case an error message will be displayed to indicate that the two values are different."
msgstr "請在「<guilabel>確認密碼</guilabel>」欄位中，輸入 <systemitem class=\"username\">admin</systemitem> 密碼。請確認「<guilabel>確認密碼</guilabel>」欄位中的值，與「<guilabel>密碼</guilabel>」欄位中的值完全相同。若輸入的值有所不同，一則錯誤訊息將會出現，並顯示這兩個值不相同。"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Select <guibutton>&lt;Apply&gt;</guibutton> and press <keycap> Enter</keycap> to save the security configuration."
msgstr "請選擇「<guibutton>&lt;套用&gt;</guibutton>」，並按下 <keycap>Enter</keycap>，以儲存安全性配置。"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The security configuration has been updated."
msgstr "安全性配置已更新。"

